Title: Last Train to Arrecife (Excerpt)
Author: Narrative Engine Example

EXT. ABANDONED RAIL YARD - PRE-DAWN

Wind skims over rusted tracks. A single warning beacon blinks against the horizon.

ELENA, 38, stands beside a dead locomotive, running her hand over a faded safety label.

RADIO (V.O.)
Storm advisory level seven. Repeat, level seven.

Elena closes her eyes, then keys the radio.

ELENA
Patch me into city control. Now.
